headline: Analysts Grow Bullish On This Data Center Play And Three More Stocks Near Buy Points
summary: As earnings season gets into full swing, what are the stocks that analysts are betting on?  Investor's Business Daily's stock screener for stocks with rising profit estimates shows four stocks that are also near buy points.  Amphenol is just below a four-weeks-tight pattern that has a buy point of 127.50, according to IBD MarketSurge.
